main event: Four oval-shaped, white, self-luminous objects were sighted in Karachi, Pakistan on April 15, 1952.
interesting points: The objects were observed at an altitude of 40,000 feet., The objects exhibited variable speeds, with a maximum speed of up to 1,000 m.p.h., The duration of the observation lasted for approximately 6 minutes., Reports indicated that the objects left a white or smoky trail., There was a significant coordination activity concerning UFO reports in Karachi during this time.
witness description: Karachi press reported several witnesses observed the objects making high-speed dives.
